{"tid":954673,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每次沖涼前都有一番掙扎","createTime":"2018-12-24T18:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T11:19:23.000Z","uid":199983,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b215149be9cbde35e46aaee5847fbfa9ea25c3c4","tid":954673,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:36:47.000Z","msg":"究竟洗唔洗頭好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唉第二朝起身特登洗一次頭好麻煩，依加洗埋都唔洗好耐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：但係等個頭乾乾地，然後再吹頭要等好耐好麻煩，我好想啲上床訓呀好L凍呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都係唔洗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：但係唔洗頭上床訓又好污穢，淨係沖涼又唔洗頭，個人一半乾淨一半污穢，好似周身唔自在咁，都係洗頭啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉屌真係好想剃光頭然後每晚用布抺下就搞掂"},{"pid":"8632782e8b816582ea5b20139c44c75e13512d87","tid":954673,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:37:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"566c3345904c5da1a8539ecb5d8957cd6eff4843","tid":954673,"uid":5883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:38:12.000Z","msg":"真係麻鳩煩啊你"},{"pid":"ecdbef7cb665e36c2ca4a8dff2d0fe6d66d47de0","tid":954673,"uid":199162,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:38:46.000Z","msg":"光頭嘅話又要煩用洗頭水定沐浴露洗頭好<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 禿頭"},{"pid":"ea219b5b58456c26b566479c73e6308dfa64fb2b","tid":954673,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:46:51.000Z","msg":"啱啱吹完頭，終於上得床<i